BARDS BARDIC

Bards are a class that are much like fighters and much like thieves, yet
not quite either. Bards play instruments and use them to sing songs that
create magical spells and bards get thier instruments by going through the
Bardic Colleges. Bards have to wield their instrument to sing spells,
which can be a bit of a disadvantage...

Here is a list of your current skills/spells at level 50:

SPELLNAME		LEVEL	COST
kick                    1       n/a
magic missile           1       10
bash                    2       n/a
block                   5       n/a
faerie fire             6       10
rescue                  8       n/a
track                   9       n/a
backstab		10	n/a
barkskin		10	20
disarm			10	n/a
