Dragons are a race of magical creatures.  They have the ability to use a 
breath weapon, fly, can see in the dark, sense living things around them, 
and are known to have tremendous strength.  Dragons are a powerful race, 
and therefore are only available to PC's as a remort option.

See Also: KNIGHT, REMORT, UNDEAD, ANGEL, THRI-KREEN, MONK
# 
DROP

If you lose interest in a carried item, you can drop it on the ground.

drop <item>
drop all.<item>
drop all
drop <number> coins

> drop bottle
> drop all.bread
> drop all
> drop 1000 coins

See also: GET, JUNK, DONATE
#
DROW DARK

Drow are a race of underground dwelling elves. They hate surface elves,
and many other races. They are strong in the arcane arts. They are quick, 
but not very strong or hearty. They can see in the dark and resist magic.

See Also: RACE
#
DRUIDS

Druids are a sect of forest dwelling lore masters.  They are at one with
nature and at home in the forest.  They possess both offensive and defensive 
spells, though usually not as powerful as their mage or cleric counterparts.
They also have the power to summon elementals, as well as unique spells
not found in other classes.

Here is a list of your spells at level 50:

