#
EXPERIENCE XP

Whenever you kill a monster or a player, you earn experience points. When
enough experience points are earned, you raise a level.
Things you should know about experience points:

  * When damaging a monster, you get experience points.

  * When killing a monster you get experience points.

  * When grouped with someone, including a mob, experience is divded by 
    level.  See help group for details.

  NOTE: If you are 10 levels lower than the average level for your group,
  you will gain only 1 exp per kill

See Also: GROUP
