Make Me Famous - This will consist of mobs that don't belong. Meaning
mobs you don't see on the mud everyday. Famous mobs and everyday pain
in the ass mobs. Each one will have a ticket that is worth points. 
Kill the mob get the ticket save for prizes. 

Rules - 
1) The mobs that have the orange tickets are for the low level players.
   Level 25 and under. ANYONE with a orange ticket over level 25 will
   be slayed. This is to give the lower levels a change to be involved
   in the quest.
2) Mobs will be placed randomly in the mud. You can not track them and
   no I will not give you the names of them. You will have to go out
   and find them. 
3) Only one mob will have a red ticket that is worth 250 points.
4) There will be no bitching and or complaining.
5) Quest will run until all tickets are found or 11pm est which ever is
   sooner.
6) All tickets must be turned in by 11pm. If you have to leave etc it
   is best you claim your prize prior to leaving.
7) Top four prizes only one of each is available. Get your tickets
   redeemed early.
8) Above is subject to change at any time it deems fit.

