#
GIANT GIANTS

Giants are a huge and powerful race. They resemble very tall and large 
humans. They do not make friends easily, but once they have given their 
friendship, they will never abandon a friend in need, no matter the danger.  
They are very strong and very hearty race. However, they are not too
intelligent and often lack common sense. Due to their size, they are somewhat
slow. They can't see in the dark; they can often "feel" the presense of people
behind them.

See Also: RACE
