"SPELL GROUP HEAL"

Usage       : cast 'group heal'
Accumulative: -
Duration    : Instantaneous

Group Heal heals everyone in the same group (and room) of the caster. It
heals just as much as the Heal spell does.

SEE ALSO: HEAL
#
"SPELL GROUP RECALL"

Usage       : cast 'group recall'
Accumulative: -
Duration    : Instantaneous

Group Recall recalls every member of the casters group who occupy the room
where the spell is cast if the caster is the leader of the group.  If the 
caster is not the leader, only the members listed above the caster on the
group list, and the caster, will recall.

SEE ALSO: GROUP, RECALL 
