HALFELF HALF-ELF HALF

Half-elves are a cross breed of elves and humans.  They are able to grow facial
hair and have extended life spans.  Their elven features are unmistakable.  
Half elves have good dexterity and their long lifespans permit them to be very
studious.  They make fine warriors, mages, and thieves. 

