 a Immortal becomes visable.

-If you are obsessive-compulsive, press 7 repeatedly at the main meun.

-If you are co-dependent, please ask someone to press 7 for you.

-If you have multipe peronalities, press ctrl, alt, delete buttons.

-If you are delusional, press the esc button and it will transfer you the
 little people in zone 8.

-If you are schizophrenic, listen carefully, and the voices will tell you
 what buttons to press.

-If you are paranoid, we know who you are. Stay online so we can finish
 tracing your IP.

-If you have amnesia, leave your char name, race, and class and password.

