IMPLEMENTORS

The implementors of Kore are Culvan, Karn, Kasmir and Zirnozz. They 
are assisted by a host of immortals, all of whom are important. You should
know though, if you really want to change the game, it helps to know how to 
suck up to the imps.

^GCulvan^n: likes anything that makes the code simpler and things that make life
easier to administrate.
^GKarn^n: like the immlist says (or at least it used to), he breaks things.
^GKasmir^n: likes tricky mobs that hit hard but also awards the player with
great equipment.
^GZirnozz^n: likes tricky mobs that hit hard but only laughs when the players
die repeatedly.

