INFORMATION INFO
There is a wealth of commands that can be used to find out more about the
world:

SCORE        Shows much info about your character
AFFECT       Shows the spells affecting your character
WHERE        Shows players in the current area
WHO          Shows all players in the game
TIME         Shows the MUD time
WEATHER      Shows the weather

POLICY       Shows the current MUD policy/rules

COMMANDS     Lists all available commands
SOCIALS      Lists all available socials
LEVELS       Lists the levels of your class and their titles
AREAS        Lists all open game areas
WIZLIST      Shows a list of administrators of this MUD
IMMLIST      Shows a list of all immortals and their duties
CHANGES      Shows a list of current code changes
AREAHELP     Displays information on documented areas
CLANHELP     Displays much information on various clan-related topics

^BNOTE: to get help on a spell, prefix it with "spell" (e.g. HELP SPELL
CHILL TOUCH)^n

