#
KING

King of the Ring (battle ring) is a four level maze. At the end of each
maze is a crystal gateway you enter it to get to the next level. On the
fourth and last level is the gateway to King of the Ring, first clan to
have a person to get there wins.

Here is the rules of do's and don't for tonights King of the Ring quest.
Any question not answered here ask an immortal.

Do's

- Clan members may group
- You may be summoned back into the arena after death. You may not be
  summoned back to a level higher then what you was on. If no one is left
  alive in your clan will be transes you back to the arena, however you
  will have to restart at level one of the battle arena.
- You can kill other clans to keep them from reaching the top.
- You may use different chars as long as they are in the same clan and
  not logged in at same time. It will be ok to summon them into the arena
  as long as it is not to a higher level then what the other char was on.
- You may heal and spellup your clannies.
  
Don't

