#
KNIGHTS

Knights are warriors who have completed a long and difficult training
to become truly powerful beings.  They possess superb attacks, massive hit
points, and the ability to heal themselves and others.  They are available
to players only as a remort option and are currently unavailable.

See Also: DRAGONS, REMORT, UNDEAD, ANGEL, THRI-KREEN
