"SPELL KNOCK"
Usage       : cast 'knock'
Accumulative: No
Duration    : lasts until reset

Knock is a powerful spell that allows mages to magically unlock all of the
doors around them. *click*!!

See Also: WIZARD LOCK
#
KORE

Kore is a mythical place in the middle of the great continent of Arda. All
around its edges, Kore is ringed by cities and hemmed in by danger. A Tyrant
now rules Kore with an iron fist, having replaced and erased the memory of
the previous king of Kore.

