"MAGIC USER" WIZARD MAGES "MAGIC-USER"
This is the class of powerful and violent magic, with spells that directly
affect the outside world, usually in the form of offensive magic that
strikes against an enemy.  Mages also possess many spells that extend their
senses magically.  Unfortunately, mages are not masters of the inner magic
and therefore cannot bless, aid, or heal themselves.

