#
SEND MAIL CHECK RECEIVE

The commands used by the Kore Mail System (KMS) are MAIL, CHECK, and
RECEIVE.  These commands can only be used while in an Official MMS Post
Office.

To write mail to Quifael:
> mail quifael

To check and see if you have any mail waiting:
> check

To ask the Postmaser to give you your mail, if you have any waiting:
> receive

Stamps cost 150 coins.

See Also: -
#
"SPELL MANA SHELL"

Usage       : cast 'mana shell'
Accumulative: No
Duration    : 6 rounds

Mana shell is one of the more powerful spells any mage can use.  It is one
of the rare defensive spells employed by magic users.  By channeling the
One Power in a shield surrounding himself, a mage can actually cause it
to absorb damage.  The effort is tiresome, and the damage absorbed will
directly impact the mage's ability to continue to channel.

See Also:
#
MANA MP

Mana is a measurement of spell power that you currently have. Mana is only
meaningful for spellcasters obviously. Higher level mages have more mana, but
they also have spells that cost more mana. Mana slowly regenerates as time
passes and regenerates faster if the caster rests and is well fed.

See Also: HIT POINT, MOVEMENT, SPELL  
#
MINOTAUR MINOTAURS

Minotaurs are a powerful race of half-man and half-bull. They are brutally
strong and hearty, but they lack foresight and vision. Due to their horrid
appearance, they are not easily welcomed in the human dominated world.
They can see in the dark; they can sense creatures around them.

See Also: RACE
#
