MEDITATE

Meditate increases the amount of mana clerics and mages regenerate each tick.
Meditate is automatically implemented by the game.  Player must be 
resting to meditate.

See Also: REST 
#
"SPELL MIRROR IMAGE"

Usage       : cast 'mirror image'
Accumulative: No (see below)
Duration    : Lasts until dispelled by blows in combat (see below)

Mirror image summons between 6 to 10 images of the spell caster. Each image
will absorb one blow in combat before it is dispelled. A caster can cast the
spell again when they already have images in order to replace the number of
images they have with perhaps a higher number.

See Also: -
# 
"SPELL MONSTER SUMMONING ONE" "SPELL MONSTER SUMMONING TWO" "SPELL MONSTER SUMMONING THREE"

Usage       : cast 'monster summoning <one|two|three>'
Accumulative: No
Duration    : Instantaneous

These spells summon a goblin, an ogre and a minotaur respectively, to fight
for you as a servant. They can be equipped and healed and make great
fighting machines. Don't abandon them though! They hate that!

See Also: -
