#
"SPELL POISON"

Usage       : cast 'poison' <victim | food | drink>
Accumulative: Yes on persons.
Duration    : 2*level hours, or permanent on food and drinks.

Casting poison on food or drink (containers) will poison it.
Eating poisoned food/drinks will poison the person eating or
drinking.

A person who is poisoned will suffer 3 times their level in damage every
hour, and gain less points than usual!!  POISON IN KORE IS DEADLY!!!

See Also: REMOVE POISON
#
POOFOUT POOFIN

When you get the spells relocate (mage, cleric and bard) or windwalk
(druid) you can set your poofin/out for different messages.

Usage: POOFIN HAS ARRIVED
       POOFOUT HAS LEFT THE BUILDING
