#
"SPELL POWER WORD STUN"

Usage       : cast 'power word stun' [victim]
Accumulative: -
Duration    : Instantaneous

If successful, power word of stun will cause the victim to fall down and
be stunned.  He or she is then extremely vulnerable to attack, and any
type of attack will do extra damage.  It is good for only one hit, however.

