#
QUEST

This simple toggle command merely informs the Powers that Be that you
wish to particpate in the currently running Quest.  If an immortal
is running a Quest and needs to know who wishes to participate, he/she
will ask players to turn on their Quest flags using this QUEST command
if they are interested in the Quest.  It also allows you to listen in on
the quest channel and receive information specific to the quest.

> quest

See Also:  QSAY, TOKENS
#
QUICKDRAW

Warrior skill.  An automatic skill: whenever an aggressive mob tries to 
attack you, you will wake up, stand and wield a weapon (if you can) and
hit the mobile before it hits you!  You can also type quickdraw while
sleeping to make yourself wake, stand, and draw a weapon.

See Also: WARRIOR
#
QUICKHEAL

Quickheal awards thieves and warriors an additional 3 hitpoints per level
each tick.  Players must be asleep to benefit this skill.

See Also: -
#
QUIT

If you have no equipment and wants to leave the mud immediately, quit is
the command to go.  To prevent accidents, if you have equipment, you can 
leave the game only by renting.

See Also: INN, RENT
