RAGE

By entering a berserk rage, a warrior increases his stamina and
attack prowess.  By doing this however, he or she chooses to fight
to the bitter end.

See Also: -
#
READ
When you want to read something.

READ is also used to read messages on bulletin boards; type HELP BOARDS
for more information.

> read note

See Also: BOARDS
#
RECALL

Unlike mercs, this circle like other circles does not have free recalls.
Just buy scrolls of recall or use the spell to recall out of battle.
The scrolls are a little spendy but you can afford it if you don't recall
too often.

See Also: -
#
RECITE SCROLL SCROLLS

Use : Recite <Scroll> [Target]

Is used to "read" a magical scroll. Target can be an object, character or
nothing (which may be yourself).

See Also: -
#
"SPELL REFRESH"

Usage       : cast 'refresh' <victim>
Accumulative: -
Duration    : Instantaneous

When cast, refresh restores movement to the victim, allowing the victim to
move further without the need for rest.

See Also: MASS REFRESH
