"SPELL WINDWALK"

Usage       : cast 'windwalk' <victim>
Accumulative: No
Duration    : Instantaneous

Provided that the caster is standing in a natural setting, windwalk will
instantaneously relocate the caster to the victim.

See Also: RELOCATE, SUMMON
#
"SPELL WIZARD LOCK"

Usage       : cast 'wizard lock'
Accumulative: No
Duration    : Permanent (see below)

This spell is used to close and lock all doors in the room. This is
useful for locking in/out players or mobs. This spell can only be 
reversed by the "Knock" spell or the "Pick" skill.

See Also: KNOCK, PICK
#
WIZLIST IMMLIST

Lists the most powerful beings on the MUD.

See Also: -
#
"SPELL WORD OF RECALL"

Usage       : cast 'word of recall' 
Accumulative: -
Duration    : Instantaneous

The caster will be transferred back to his sanctuary (presently
the Temple of Vulmarta).

See Also: RECALL 
#
"SPELL WORD OF DEATH"

Usage       : cast 'word of death' <victim>
Accumulation: -
Damage      : unknown
Duration    : Instantaneous

It is said that a high level mage can kill with a single word.  
This is the most powerful spell known in the realm of Kore.  With this 
spell dragons have been slain, kings overthrown, and mighty warriors 
reduced to ash.

See Also: MAGE
#
WRITE

In order to write a note, you need a piece of blank paper (or similar), and
a pen of some sort. You can then type something like "write on the paper with
the pen", whereupon you'll be asked to type in your note at the keyboard.

WRITE is also used to post messages to bulletin boards.  Type HELP BOARDS
for more information.

See Also: BOARDS
#~
 
